	.  This Agreement will be effective as of the date hereof and shall terminate on the later of (i) the date on which there is no longer a New Class II Director serving on the Board and (ii) the date that is two (2) years from the date hereof (such termination date, the 

	Termination Date

	);

	provided

	that the provisions of this Section 6 shall survive such termination.



	 




