	solely for the purpose of calculating the registration fee pursuant to Rule 457(c) under the Securities Act, based on the average of the
	high and low prices of our Class A common stock on the New York Stock Exchange on March 1, 2016. The proposed maximum offering price per share of Class A common stock will be
	determined from time to time by the selling stockholders named herein, or such additional selling stockholders as may be named in one or more prospectus supplements, in connection with, and at the
	time of, the sale by such selling stockholders of the shares of Class A common stock registered hereunder.






