	Table of Contents







	




	whether the shares of the series will be convertible into shares of any other class or series, or any other security, of our Company
	or any other corporation, and, if so, the specification of the other class or series or other security, the conversion price or prices or rate or rates, any rate adjustments, the date or dates as of
	which the shares will be convertible and all other terms and conditions upon which the conversion may be made;








	




